passages.name: name
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[errorCoInsured]]"
          when="coInsured > 6"
>
</Redirect>

<Message>
  {DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_NAME_MESSAGE_1}
</Message>

<TextActionSet next="[[{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_CONTINUE}->birthDate]]">
  <TextAction title="{DK_CONTENT_NAME_TEXT_ACTION_TITLE_FIRST_NAME}"
              placeholder="{DK_CONTENT_NAME_TEXT_ACTION_PLACEHOLDER_FIRST_NAME}"
              large="true"
              key="firstName"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="{DK_CONTENT_NAME_TEXT_ACTION_TITLE_SURNAME}"
              placeholder="{DK_CONTENT_NAME_TEXT_ACTION_PLACEHOLDER_SURNAME}"
              large="true"
              key="lastName"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: NewsletterSuccess
passages.text: Double-click this passage to edit it.

passages.name: studentEligibilityCheck
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[Offer]]"
          when="birthDate.Age > 30 || livingSpace > 50 || coInsured > 0"
          key="isStudent"
          value="false"
>
</Redirect>

<Redirect to="[[student]]"
          when="true"
>
</Redirect>

passages.name: address
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[errorSize]]"
          when="size > 250"
>
</Redirect>

<Message>
  {DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_ADDRESS_MESSAGE_1}
</Message>

<Response>
  {street}, {zipCode}
</Response>

<TextActionSet next="[[{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_CONTINUE}->coInsured]]">
  <TextAction title="{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_ADDRESS_TEXT_ACTION_TITLE_ADDRESS}"
              placeholder="{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_ADDRESS_PLACEHOLDER}"
              large="true"
              key="street"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_ADDRESS_TEXT_ACTION_TITLE_ZIP_CODE}"
              mask="NorwegianPostalCode"
              placeholder="{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_ZIP_CODE_PLACEHOLDER}"
              key="zipCode"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: Offer
passages.text:
<Message>
  {DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_OFFER_MESSAGE_1}
</Message>

<GraphQLApi next="[[OfferSuccess]]">
  <Mutation>
    mutation CreateDanishQuote(
    $id: ID!,
	$firstName: String!,
	$lastName: String!,
	$birthDate: LocalDate!,
	$email: String!,
	$coInsured: Int!,
	$livingSpace: Int!,
	$street: String!,
	$zipCode: String!
	$type: DanishHomeContentsType!,
	$isStudent: Boolean!
  ) {
    createQuote(input: {
      id: $id,
	  firstName: $firstName,
	  lastName: $lastName,
	  birthDate: $birthDate,
	  email: $email,
	  danishHomeContents: {
	    coInsured: $coInsured,
		livingSpace: $livingSpace,
		street: $street,
		zipCode: $zipCode,
		type: $type,
		isStudent: $isStudent
	  }
    }) {
      ... on CompleteQuote {
        id
		insuranceCost {
		  monthlyGross {
			amount
		    currency
		  }
		  monthlyDiscount {
			amount
		    currency
		  }
		  monthlyNet {
		    amount
		    currency
		  }
        }
	  }
	}
  }
  </Mutation>
  <GeneratedVariable key="id"
                     type="uuid"
                     storeas="quoteId"
  >
  </GeneratedVariable>
  <Variable key="firstName"
            from="firstName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="lastName"
            from="lastName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="birthDate"
            from="birthDate"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="email"
            from="email"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="coInsured"
            from="coInsured"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="livingSpace"
            from="livingSpace"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="street"
            from="street"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="zipCode"
            from="zipCode"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="type"
            from="type"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="isStudent"
            from="isStudent"
            as="boolean"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Error next="[[offerError]]">
  </Error>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.amount"
          as="monthlyGross"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.currency"
          as="monthlyGrossCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.amount"
          as="monthlyNet"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.currency"
          as="monthlyNetCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.amount"
          as="monthlyDiscount"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.currency"
          as="monthlyDiscountCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
</GraphQLApi>
